name: Conspiracy No.001 | 2080 Love Story
description: I'm starting a series called Conspiracy. The root meaning of conspiracy is "to breathe together." The start of the new decade has made it impossible for a lot of us to breathe together in physical space. This emerging cryptoart community has given us a chance to breathe together with our art. Conspire. Co-inspire. For this first piece the conspirators were: @AriasJopet, @NitroFux, @3vilyn_3V, @BBStudiosGuild, @_khimba
